  "text": "Can you define what you mean by a crystallized entity? I am Ra. We have used this particular term because it has a fairly precise meaning in your language when a christoline structure is formed of your physical material. The elements present in each molecule are bonded in a regularized fashion with the elements in each other molecule. Thus the structure is regular and when a fully and perfectly crystallized has certain properties. It will not splinter or break. It is a very strong without effort, and it is radiant traducing light into a beautiful refraction giving pleasure of the eye to many.",
